						<summary>

						<p>This is damaged. It seems to record some gift made by Vēṭṭandai Seṭṭi <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Gaṇavadiyāṇḍāṉ a merchant of Pūndamalli in Puliyūr-kōṭṭam for the early morning service of the deity and for burning two lamps at the time in the temple at Gōvindavāḍi.</p>						

